LAGOS – Following the recent controversy trailing the actual age of former Governor of Lagos State and National Leader of the All Progressives Congress, APC, Asiwaju Bola Ahmed Tinubu, Senator Shehu Sani has come out to declare that the 2023 Presidential aspirant of the ruling party is not as old as he is perceived to be by many. According to Sani who made the statement on his official, verified twitter handle, @ShehuSani, himself and Tinubu are actually agemates. He wrote; “Jagaban is not as old as you portray him. We are both young guys and age mates.” 2023: I Never Endorsed Tinubu’s Presidential Ambition,… I Will Be Next Governor Of Kaduna – Shehu Sani Boasts See his tweet below;